en.title: FE Making Waves in the Philippines!
en.content:
REPORT FROM FE'S PHILIPPINES PRESIDENTIAL DIRECTOR PASTOR ART MEDINA.

Our FE West Avenue, Quezon City (Metro Manila) office is doing regular daily BEPs. Our BIG BEPs are on Tuesdays and Thursdays.

Picture #1: Tuesday BEP with 150 guests from different cities of Metro Manila who came upon the invitation of our active FE Leaders like Philip Ciocon who is speaking on the stage. Seated among the guests are FE Directors Mae Heredia, Art and Grace Tuason, Jay Lastima, Pastor Ronnie Yap, Doctor Dino Ruiz, Retired Brig General Federico Ruiz, among others.

Picture #2: FE Director Mae Heredia with Movie Actress Ara Mina (in orange shirt), Mrs Sonia Mathay and Chiqui Mathay. With FE's Quantum Pendant on, the four ladies were able to lift the heavyweight man with ease!
 
Tuesday BEP with 150 guests from different cities of Metro Manila who came upon the invitation of our active FE Leaders like Philip Ciocon who is speaking on the stage. Seated among the guests are FE Directors Mae Heredia, Art and Grace Tuason, Jay Lastima, Pastor Ronnie Yap, Doctor Dino Ruiz, Retired Brig General Federico Ruiz, among others.
FE Director Mae Heredia with Movie Actress Ara Mina (in orange shirt), Mrs Sonia Mathay and Chiqui Mathay. With FE's Quantum Pendant on, the four ladies were able to lift the heavyweight man with ease!
